data.description: Wonderful 2014 built Taylor Morrison, all brick,1 story home. Beautiful island kitchen opens to the spacious living area. Granite counters. SS appliances including a gas cooktop. Living area has high ceilings, stone accented wood burning fireplace & double French doors leading to the covered patio. Wall of windows to the back patio make the room light & bright. Flanking the tiled entry foyer is formal dining room space with chair rail molding +direct access to the kitchen. Study off the living space has French doors for additional privacy or perhaps could even serve as an extra bedroom. Large primary bedroom to the rear of the home has bay windows w/great views of the private back yard. Lots of trees in the neighborhood behind the house make this an especially appealing lot & yard. Extensive community amenities include hike & bike trails, recently expanded to Deussen Park,2 pools, tennis & pickleball & convenient to shopping, restaurants & schools. Washer/dryer & refrigerator included.
